      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 4 for MRL 5 device.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions was applied to the Navier-Stokes solver but not to the scalar hemolysis transport equation; achieved level 3 falls short of required level 4."
    },
