      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 4 for MRL 5 device.",
      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation performed on three systematically refined meshes; grid convergence index computed but temporal discretization error not formally separated, limiting achieved level to 3."
