      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 3 for MRL 5 device.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro test conditions partially replicate VAD operating range; blood analog fluid properties and temperature control documented but physiologic hematocrit variability not characterized, giving achieved level 2."
    },
