      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 4 for MRL 5 device.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis is the primary QoI and is clinically relevant; however, secondary QoIs such as platelet activation and thrombogenic potential are not addressed, limiting achieved level to 3."
