      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 4 for MRL 5 device.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities used the FDA generic pump geometry rather than a patient-specific VAD design; geometric and operational similarity arguments are qualitative only, yielding achieved level 2."
    },
