      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 3 for MRL 5 device.",
      "rationale": "No formal user error analysis or operator qualification study has been conducted for this simulation workflow; identified as epistemic gap, achieved level defaulted to 1."
